sources.title: The Jimmy Show - Full Movie
sources.description:
Jimmy O'Brien's (Frank Whaley, 'Pulp Fiction') dead-end job in the grocery store stockroom has him feeling powerless and unfulfilled, but one successful night at a local stand-up open mic gives Jimmy a glimpse into the career he never knew he wanted. Starring Carla Gugino ('Watchmen') and Ethan Hawke ('Training Day').
